fields.profile_description: Motivated enthusiastic developer,I constantly seek to improve my skills through leaving my comfort zone, I love facing new problems and solving them, hard worker, CODING EVERYDAY!
fields.skills_description: Coding turned from an intriguing subject to an undevided aspect of my life since I first tried my hand at it back in 2014, started with C++, Java, Different Web Languages, Python, But my Eternal love is JAVA! In the other hand, Databases modeling and conception runs in my veins.
fields.about_intro: I am CHAGUETMI Yousr ELLAH Wassim, born in June 1995, in love with IT since childhood, diving deeper in coding each day. Licence degree in Information Systems and Software Engineering, working on my Master on Natural Language Processing.

fields.description: Designed and realised a decisional software for the small industry company, it manages the whole information system (employees, products, clients, deliveries...), since it wasn't that big i worked on it alone.
As a freelancer, my experience in android mobile developement was needed as out-sourcing, to help the local dev team to accomplish the migration of the company's delivery app.
Developed a decisional matrix as an academic project.

In a team of four, we developed a food delivery platform for the university, it had a restaurant side, client side and admin side, we did a web and mobile interface for each side, and i was in change of the database modeling and conception.
Developed a web platform for trips' booking with pure PHP.
developed a web platform and a mobile app, for events management, using Laravel and Android.
I lead the junior dev team, modelised and concepted the database, of an application for freelancer touristic guides in Algeria, we had the 3rd place.

I manage information systems and project's backends, both web (django) and mobile (android), as I model the database, make backend functionalities, improve performance, build REST Apis to be consumed by the mobile apps.
